</p></entry></row></thead><tbody class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">1 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Open buffer door. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-7FED32C9-2FE2-487F-A545-D7AB7BC5301E" class="- topic/fig "><title class="- topic/title ">Old </title><image href="GUID-2499D72C-C090-40E1-9C08-D6C6101C4CB2-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-2499D72C-C090-40E1-9C08-D6C6101C4CB2-low.png"/></fig><fig id="GUID-3BEF471D-1B42-499A-9DAE-BEBBCBDC06D3" class="- topic/fig "><title class="- topic/title ">New</title><image href="GUID-E47F8134-1F1A-4980-9F84-B403D6757D17-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-E47F8134-1F1A-4980-9F84-B403D6757D17-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">2 
