</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-374378C3-4F0F-4ADB-82A8-F6ED568DD408" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-DC4E1C20-815E-40B5-82CA-4346758BC533-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-DC4E1C20-815E-40B5-82CA-4346758BC533-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">3 
